# 📊 Insurance Analytics Dashboard (Power BI)

🚀 Turning insurance data into actionable insights with Power BI.

---

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is an interactive **Insurance Analytics Dashboard** built using **Power BI**, inspired by PolicyBazaar data.  

The dashboard helps in analyzing insurance policies, insured values, risk coverage, and regional trends to support **data-driven decision making**.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze total number of policies and insured value  
- Understand regional performance of insurance data  
- Identify risk coverage patterns  
- Compare rural vs urban insurance distribution  
- Provide insights for business growth  

---

## 📊 Key Features
- 📈 KPI Cards (Total Policies, Premium, Insured Value)  
- 🌍 Region-wise Analysis (Central, East, Midwest, Northeast)  
- 🏙️ Rural vs Urban Segmentation  
- 🧾 Business Type & Industry Breakdown  
- ⚖️ Risk Coverage Analysis (Yes / No)  
- 🗺️ Map Visualization for location insights  

---

